column5: Just booked a fly in with luenenburgers to Whittle lake. Wondering if anyone on the board knows anything about this place. Friend wants a day or 2 of brookies, I just want to be rewarded with 100's of stupid eyes and pike! Any help would be appreciated.  D

Been there twice and most recent last June. I'll fill you in as much as I can about the lake when I return from holidays, if I forget pm me and i'll do so then. I have lots of pics and maps I can pass along to you as well. If you search Whittle Lake on the forum you'll find my latest report. You will have a great time up there and won't find a nicer camp anywhere for a fly-in.  Mike
Now I am even more excited! Cant wait. Ill pm you  Thanks
i have been to keg lake main lodge 5 times luenenburgers treat you like gold you will have trip of your life
